{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0672a4b899","title":"对《林彪同志给浙江省军区的指示》的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5f7c1f51f3","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":29,"articleId":"0672a4b899"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0181bafc77","type":"title","text":"对《林彪同志给浙江省军区的指示》的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"2228a80e59","type":"paragraph","text":"此件应发到全军营以上各级机关去，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"8a6f8473ad","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"5787b97896","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年十二月二十九日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0672a4b899"}],"page":{"id":"2d953b4720","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0672a4b899","start":243,"end":243}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"04c12e0517","type":"paragraph","text":"三、从头到尾要贯彻对学生热情、友好、耐心的态度，在耐心的问题上，军队要做出榜样，听到反面的话，绝不能粗暴、发脾气。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"0eef554058","type":"paragraph","text":"要把学生的工作当作群众工作来做，这是送上门来的群众工作，不但不应当由于这个问题引起军队和革命学生的对抗，而且应当借这个机会，大力加强军队与革命学生的团结。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"3e98fa9fef","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"4af43e46e8","type":"paragraph","text":"附：林彪同志给浙江省军区的指示","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"7b54148720","type":"paragraph","text":"一、领导同志要挺身而出，同群众见面，既不能躲，也不能压，越躲越压越糟糕。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"8dfed45360","type":"subdate","text":"一九六六年十二月二十九日","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"9663703f0e","type":"paragraph","text":"此件应发到全军营以上各级机关去。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"b50d6743ab","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：这是一九六六年十二月二十九日浙江军区杜平用电话向林彪同志报告了省军区与浙江红色造反联络站谈判情况后，当天下午五点半钟林彪同志作出的重要指示。）","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"c55485994b","type":"paragraph","text":"处理这个问题的原则要重申以下三条：","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"d91bd519b7","type":"paragraph","text":"二、对学生提出的正确批评，要诚恳接受，完全接受，自己做错了的，要坦率地进行自我批评。他们的合理要求，凡能做到的要完全做到。对他们不正确的意见和不合理的要求，要进行解释和教育。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"},{"id":"fa90140d4a","type":"title","text":"对《林彪同志给浙江省军区的指示》的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899"}],"page":{"id":"157a176825","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0672a4b899","start":541,"end":542}}}},"__N_SSG":true}